            <author><name>Hannah Ritchie</name></author>
            <summary><![CDATA[Excess mortality has become a key metric to understand the true impact of the Coronavirus pandemic. But how is excess mortality measured; and what can we learn from cross-country comparisons? Janine Aron and John Muellbauer provide an overview on excess mortality statistics.<br><br><a href="https://ourworldindata.org/covid-excess-mortality" target="_blank"><img src="https://ourworldindata.org/app/uploads/2020/06/Figure-3-768x566.png"/></a>]]></summary>
